1324
01:21:48,440 --> 01:21:51,480
No matter how good it tastes, the mouth will feel soupy.

1325
01:21:51,980 --> 01:21:55,750
In the end, she needs something to refute it.

1326
01:22:01,320 --> 01:22:02,420
- What is that? - What is that?

1327
01:22:04,620 --> 01:22:06,230
- It must be shrimp. - Is it shrimp?

1328
01:22:07,060 --> 01:22:08,930
It must be small like whitebait.

1329
01:22:09,060 --> 01:22:10,359
Small shrimp.

1330
01:22:10,360 --> 01:22:12,629
- I see. Small shrimp. - You know, the small ones.

1331
01:22:12,630 --> 01:22:14,330
