1334
01:22:23,580 --> 01:22:25,680
I wanted to find the best-quality shrimp.

1335
01:22:25,810 --> 01:22:28,320
I searched all the dried fish places.

1336
01:22:28,720 --> 01:22:31,349
I asked to see the shrimp and took a sniff too.

1337
01:22:31,350 --> 01:22:33,389
One place had really good shrimp.

1338
01:22:33,390 --> 01:22:34,850
I knew they were it.

1339
01:22:35,060 --> 01:22:37,419
I bought them...

1340
01:22:37,420 --> 01:22:39,659
