1343
01:22:49,170 --> 01:22:51,670
I sifted it to make it super fine.

1344
01:22:57,310 --> 01:23:01,280
The name of my bread is Pain Au Shrimp.

1345
01:23:01,580 --> 01:23:04,279
I have the ambition to make a bread...

1346
