1348
01:23:10,490 --> 01:23:12,160
- It's imitation crab. - Is it imitation crab?

1349
01:23:12,390 --> 01:23:14,829
It looks like a Viennoiserie in the shape of a shrimp.

1350
01:23:14,830 --> 01:23:15,830
- Is that the dough? - The dough.

1351
01:23:15,831 --> 01:23:17,099
- It's not imitation crab, is it? - Is it dough?

1352
01:23:17,100 --> 01:23:18,799
- It looks like imitation crab. - It really does.

1353
01:23:18,800 --> 01:23:20,200
It's indistinguishable.

1354
01:23:29,510 --> 01:23:32,150
It's a shrimp bread, so it should be shrimp-shaped.

1355
01:23:34,910 --> 01:23:38,990
I took the powder and rolled it in the pastry dough.

1356
01:23:40,920 --> 01:23:42,690
It really looks like shrimp.

1357
01:23:42,960 --> 01:23:44,489
What a fantastic idea.

1358
01:23:44,490 --> 01:23:46,060
- Gosh. - It's so cute.

1359
01:23:47,460 --> 01:23:49,459
I think his idea is even crazier.

1360
01:23:49,460 --> 01:23:50,500
You're right.

1361
01:23:52,500 --> 01:23:54,799
Everyone will think it looks like a shrimp.

1362
01:23:54,800 --> 01:23:57,040
That's my bread's strength.

1363
01:24:02,980 --> 01:24:07,809
Kim Si Yeob is someone with a lot of technical skills.

1364
01:24:07,810 --> 01:24:09,719
But such people...

1365
01:24:09,720 --> 01:24:12,389
