1377
01:24:58,230 --> 01:25:01,230
It will bring out the intuitive Shrimp Chips' taste.

1378
01:25:01,370 --> 01:25:03,670
It's salty and savory, so it will taste good.

1379
01:25:11,380 --> 01:25:15,749
How should I reinterpret it to make it fun?

1380
01:25:15,750 --> 01:25:18,120
That thought boosted my dopamine.

1381
01:25:19,420 --> 01:25:21,520
- She's stamping? - Stamping?

1382
01:25:21,790 --> 01:25:22,820
- Amazing. - Is it chocolate?

1383
01:25:28,430 --> 01:25:29,560
I'm going to win.

1384
01:25:30,430 --> 01:25:31,699
How will it taste?

1385
01:25:31,700 --> 01:25:33,569
She'll become a strong contender.

1386
01:25:33,570 --> 01:25:35,599
- I'm curious. - Shrimp with caramel?

1387
01:25:35,600 --> 01:25:36,940
- Sweet and salty. - Sweet and salty.

1388
01:25:44,710 --> 01:25:45,750
It's done.

1389
01:25:51,180 --> 01:25:52,420
I gave it my all.

1390
01:25:52,620 --> 01:25:55,149
If you try your very best,

1391
01:25:55,150 --> 01:25:56,420
