1392
01:26:02,730 --> 01:26:05,029
- I think that's tartar sauce. - Shrimp and cucumbers go well too.

1393
01:26:05,030 --> 01:26:06,300
- Tartar sauce! - Yes.

1394
01:26:13,470 --> 01:26:15,110
- That'll taste good no matter what. - I know, right?

1395
01:26:15,210 --> 01:26:17,340
- I could just eat it with a spoon. - Exactly.

1396
01:26:40,300 --> 01:26:41,430
I'm finished.

1397
01:27:02,060 --> 01:27:06,090
I had so many shrimps and Shrimp Chips while preparing.

1398
01:27:06,660 --> 01:27:09,800
I think this much effort deserves a win.

1399
01:27:12,400 --> 01:27:14,600
I'll show everyone who's the real crazy one around here.

1400
01:27:15,200 --> 01:27:17,540
Bring it on. I can win against anyone.

1401
01:27:20,470 --> 01:27:23,080
Let us see how the Shrimp Chips...

1402
01:27:23,340 --> 01:27:25,210
