1404
01:27:31,450 --> 01:27:33,090
- I was most excited for these two. - Me too.

1405
01:27:33,690 --> 01:27:37,020
I think it's more intriguing because it's a match between bread and cake.

1406
01:27:38,260 --> 01:27:40,330
- A match between bread and cake. - Bread and cake.

1407
01:27:42,960 --> 01:27:44,599
We're all curious...

1408
01:27:44,600 --> 01:27:46,870
