1409
01:27:46,970 --> 01:27:49,840
Will Contender Hwang Ji Oh reveal her bread first?

1410
01:27:52,610 --> 01:27:53,670
My gosh!

1411
01:27:55,270 --> 01:27:56,380
It's a cake.

1412
01:27:58,610 --> 01:27:59,980
- It's so beautiful. - A cake?

1413
01:28:00,550 --> 01:28:03,650
