1414
01:28:03,820 --> 01:28:06,150
- The name is First Snow Shrimp. - First Snow Shrimp?

1415
01:28:07,450 --> 01:28:11,120
Yes, First Snow Shrimp is the name of the cake I made.

1416
01:28:12,460 --> 01:28:14,260
Before embarking on this new challenge for myself,

1417
01:28:14,790 --> 01:28:17,329
I tried to think about the things that would be new...

1418
01:28:17,330 --> 01:28:18,770
