1426
01:28:41,720 --> 01:28:44,960
The shrimp chocolate in the middle also symbolizes the shrimp in snow.

1427
01:28:49,960 --> 01:28:51,959
I really liked the story you put into your cake.

1428
01:28:51,960 --> 01:28:55,099
These stories can get too cheesy or far-fetched sometimes,

1429
01:28:55,100 --> 01:28:57,270
but yours was very touching and interesting.

1430
01:28:58,270 --> 01:29:00,440
Next, Contender Kim Si Yeob.

1431
01:29:06,410 --> 01:29:07,950
- It looks like a shrimp. - A big one.

1432
01:29:09,150 --> 01:29:10,550
It's a really big shrimp!

1433
01:29:11,250 --> 01:29:13,320
My bread is called Pain Au Shrimp.

1434
01:29:13,620 --> 01:29:15,020
It's based on a pain au suisse,

1435
01:29:15,520 --> 01:29:17,690
