1438
01:29:23,860 --> 01:29:26,570
While doing that, I also mixed my soul in it.

1439
01:29:27,470 --> 01:29:30,600
- This bread has my soul in it. - That's funny.

1440
01:29:33,210 --> 01:29:35,640
The theme was to use Korean wheat.

1441
01:29:35,810 --> 01:29:37,879
I wanted to prove that you can also bake croissants...

1442
01:29:37,880 --> 01:29:40,680
