1447
01:29:53,390 --> 01:29:54,530
- I look forward to having it. - Yes.

1448
01:29:54,730 --> 01:29:56,500
- I really like pastries too. - Really?

1449
01:29:56,630 --> 01:29:57,960
More calories mean more flavor.

1450
01:29:58,700 --> 01:29:59,700
That's true.

1451
01:30:00,230 --> 01:30:01,629
I heard Contender Kim Si Yeob...

1452
01:30:01,630 --> 01:30:03,499
