1461
01:30:29,830 --> 01:30:32,200
My goodness, it's so beautiful.

1462
01:30:32,930 --> 01:30:34,030
Oh, my, how pretty!

1463
01:30:34,300 --> 01:30:36,069
- I can't imagine how it'll taste. - Me neither.

1464
01:30:36,070 --> 01:30:37,070
At all.

1465
01:30:40,310 --> 01:30:41,570
The smell is quite powerful.

1466
01:30:43,710 --> 01:30:44,810
Gosh, I can smell the shrimp!

1467
01:31:07,800 --> 01:31:10,070
It's good. It's really good.

1468
01:31:12,070 --> 01:31:13,369
On the outside, it looks very classy...

1469
01:31:13,370 --> 01:31:14,669
- and expensive. - Yes.

1470
01:31:14,670 --> 01:31:17,310
