1473
01:31:22,720 --> 01:31:24,980
I think this bread can be quite dangerous.

1474
01:31:28,420 --> 01:31:31,020
The overall balance and the texture are all too good.

1475
01:31:31,360 --> 01:31:33,660
I don't think I'll be able to stop eating this.

1476
01:31:34,560 --> 01:31:37,299
It was a great viennoiserie as well.

1477
01:31:37,300 --> 01:31:42,200
Even though a lot of moisture is in the bread because of the filling,

1478
01:31:42,340 --> 01:31:44,600
