- Thank you. - Yes.

1487
01:32:09,800 --> 01:32:11,460
I didn't really mind what the Masters said about his bread.

1488
01:32:11,800 --> 01:32:14,030
I thought my cake was delicious enough to win over all of that.

1489
01:32:14,430 --> 01:32:15,870
It tasted fine to me.

1490
01:32:18,140 --> 01:32:19,969
Next, Contender Hwang Ji Oh.

1491
01:32:19,970 --> 01:32:22,340
