1509
01:33:44,090 --> 01:33:45,760
But your cake isn't fishy at all.

1510
01:33:47,430 --> 01:33:49,060
It was such a creative idea.

1511
01:33:49,960 --> 01:33:51,429
I tried the cake seperately first,

1512
01:33:51,430 --> 01:33:53,800
